high_descs: Go forward to the counter that is between the coffee maker and sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn left to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn to the left, go forward to face the dishwasher.
Put the knife in the third drawer down to the left of the dishwasher.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Walk forward to the large knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn left towards the dishwasher and walk forward very slightly.
Put the knife in the middle drawer to the left of the dishwasher and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned knife in a drawer.
